sols_latex:
Noting that $f(x_1) = 0$, we solve for $x_1$ using the equation of the
tangent line to $f$ at $(x_0, f(x_0))$:

\begin{align*}
y - y_0 &= m(x - x_0)
\\ f(x_1) - f(x_0) &= f'(x_0)(x_1 - x_0)
\\ 0 - f(x_0) &= f'(x_0)(x_1 - x_0)
\\ x_1 &= { \color{blue} x_0 - \frac{f(x_0)}{f'(x_0)} }
\end{align*}

which is answer ${\color{blue}\text{(E)}}$.

